metadata.name: Early Visions
metadata.description:
Going live at 11 am EST.

This first series is the beginning of a larger project that will allow my work to come to life in this new space.

- There will be 6 burn events in the next few days.  
- Many owners will also receive the physical version and signed by the artist. 
- Finally this series will remain and be  will be a pass for the next series to reward my early supporters.  

Remember to only buy if you like the art.
